<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 00:56:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国嫦娥六号探测器从月球背面升空</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-change-6-probe-lifts-off-far-side-moon-2024-06-04/</link><description>官方媒体新华社周二宣布，中国嫦娥六号探测器已从月球背面升空，开始返回地球的旅程。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 00:14:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-change-6-probe-lifts-off-far-side-moon-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>澳门赌场发挥最佳牌力赢得优质客户</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/macau-casinos-play-best-hands-win-over-premium-customers-2024-06-03/</link><description>来到澳门的顾客类型发生变化，规模较小的赌场运营商美高梅中国和永利澳门获得了回报，而规模较大的竞争对手金沙中国和银河娱乐则急于迎头赶上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 23:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/macau-casinos-play-best-hands-win-over-premium-customers-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：欧洲人的国际原子能机构决议草案向伊朗施压，要求其处理颗粒物和检查人员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/europeans-submit-draft-resolution-iran-iaea-board-2024-06-03/</link><description>欧洲列强周一向联合国核监督机构理事会提交了一项决议草案，要求本周进行投票，再次迫使伊朗解释在未申报地点发现的铀痕迹，并涵盖了禁止检查人员等问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 21:59:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/europeans-submit-draft-resolution-iran-iaea-board-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲 增长担忧加剧，“坏消息就是坏消息”？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-03/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 21:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>达赖喇嘛办公室称本月将访问美国接受膝盖治疗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/dalai-lama-visit-us-knee-treatment-this-month-his-office-says-2024-06-03/</link><description>西藏精神领袖达赖喇嘛的办公室周一表示，他将于本月前往美国接受膝盖治疗，并且从 6 月 20 日起将不再举行平常的公开活动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:51:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/dalai-lama-visit-us-knee-treatment-this-month-his-office-says-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部高级官员前往罗马就债务和俄罗斯资产进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/senior-us-treasury-official-heads-rome-talks-debt-russian-assets-2024-06-03/</link><description>美国财政部发言人周一表示，美国财政部高级国际官员将于本周在罗马会见意大利官员，在七国集团领导人峰会之前讨论俄罗斯被冻结的资产，并在梵蒂冈主导的活动中就发展中国家债务问题发表讲话。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/senior-us-treasury-official-heads-rome-talks-debt-russian-assets-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>瑞典第七AP基金不包括沙特阿美公司和其他六家公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/swedens-seventh-ap-fund-excludes-saudi-aramco-six-other-companies-2024-06-03/</link><description>瑞典第七 AP 基金 (AP7) 养老基金经理周一表示，由于石油开采或煤炭生产领域的大规模业务，该基金已将沙特阿美公司和其他六家公司从其投资组合中列入黑名单。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 11:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/swedens-seventh-ap-fund-excludes-saudi-aramco-six-other-companies-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>工党发言人在英国上市前会见了 Shein</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/labour-party-has-met-with-shein-ahead-potential-uk-listing-spokesperson-2024-06-03/</link><description>人们普遍预计将在英国下一次选举中掌权的工党表示，在伦敦上市之前，工党已与中国创办的快时尚制造商 Shein 进行了会面。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 11:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/labour-party-has-met-with-shein-ahead-potential-uk-listing-spokesperson-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰战争：瑞士基辅和平条款峰会有何期待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-expect-swiss-summit-ukraines-peace-terms-2024-06-03/</link><description>瑞士将于6月15日至16日主办峰会，旨在为乌克兰总统泽连斯基的和平提议争取广泛的国际支持，其中包括俄罗斯军队从乌克兰全面撤军，但莫斯科尚未受到邀请。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-expect-swiss-summit-ukraines-peace-terms-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：华尔街关注充满选举的六月就业周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:03:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>尽管伊朗愤怒，中国仍坚持对有争议的海湾岛屿的立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-maintains-stance-disputed-gulf-islands-despite-irans-anger-2024-06-03/</link><description>尽管德黑兰对北京将伊朗控制的岛屿描述为需要与阿拉伯联合酋长国解决的问题感到愤怒，但中国周一在海湾三个有争议的岛屿上坚持了立场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-maintains-stance-disputed-gulf-islands-despite-irans-anger-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示所有努力都应在俄乌和平措施中得到认可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-says-all-efforts-should-be-recognised-russia-ukraine-peace-measures-2024-06-03/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周一表示，中方认为，支持围绕俄乌战争采取和平措施的一切努力都应得到认可。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-says-all-efforts-should-be-recognised-russia-ukraine-peace-measures-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>腾讯、腾讯音乐拟7000万美元入股泰国GMM音乐10%股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-tencent-music-value-thailands-gmm-music-700-mln-with-stake-buy-2024-06-03/</link><description>泰国娱乐平台GMM Music周一表示，腾讯和腾讯音乐娱乐将以7000万美元收购该公司10%的股份，巩固其分拆计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 06:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-tencent-music-value-thailands-gmm-music-700-mln-with-stake-buy-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>继中国之后，Zara 将直播购物实验扩展到欧洲和美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/after-china-zara-expands-live-shopping-experiment-europe-us-2024-06-03/</link><description>Zara今年将把直播购物扩展到英国、欧洲和美国，测试一种在中国已经广受欢迎但西方购物者不太熟悉的模式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/after-china-zara-expands-live-shopping-experiment-europe-us-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：工厂繁忙，市场情绪乐观</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-03/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 04:35:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>